OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPressure builds on Rishi   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FSunak to act now on living 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcosts                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The chancellor must act now and not    
OL,6, wait for the Autumn Budget to help     
OL,7, people with the soaring cost of living,
OL,8, say business groups and unions.        
OL,10,FThe Confederation of British Industry  
OL,11,Fsaid: "There are some choices about    
OL,12,Fwhat you do now and what you do later. 
OL,13,FYou have to help the hardest hit now." 
OL,15,FRishi Sunak has said the government    
OL,16,Fwill act where it can but said it will 
OL,17,Fnot be easy to cut costs for families. 
OL,19,FUK inflation is at a 40-year high of 9%
OL,20,Fas energy, food and fuel prices soar.  
